          leftAdjointCompIso adj‚ÇÄ‚ÇÇ adj‚ÇÇ‚ÇÉ adj‚ÇÄ‚ÇÉ e‚ÇÄ‚ÇÇ‚ÇÉ := by
  rw [leftAdjointCompIso‚ÇÄ‚ÇÅ‚ÇÉ_eq_conjugateIsoEquiv_symm,
